(% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial sans-serif; font-size: 0.6em&amp;#34; %)Our industrial civilization is at a crossroads. Oil and the other fossil fuel energies that make up the industrial way …impacting the very way we conduct business, govern society, educate our children, and engage in civic life.

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in; &amp;#34; %)
