(% style=&amp;#34;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial sans-serif; font-size: 0.6em&amp;#34; %)An overt political challenge is a necessary component of this strategy.  The plan’s confrontation with status quo energy elites galvanizes movements and lends legitimacy to broader environmental movements. 

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in; &amp;#34; %)
(% style=&amp;#34;color:#222222;&amp;#34; %) 

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in; &amp;#34; %)
